iant of   Dev ."],"variants":[{"name":"Deborah","meanings":["Biblical name (meaning ‘bee’ in Hebrew), borne by the nurse of Rebecca (Genesis 35:8) and by a woman judge and prophet (Judges 4–5) who led the Israelites to victory over the Canaanites. It has always been popular as a Jewish name. It was in use among Christians by the mid 16th century and was taken up by the Puritans in the 17th century, in part because the bee was a symbol of industriousness. Since then it has enjoyed enormous popularity, peaking in the 1960s. Among other famous bearers is the actress  Deborah Kerr  (  1921–2007 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Gilbert de Ursewyke was born in 1125 as the son of Bernulph de Ursewyke. He had at least 1 son."},"et":{"1125–":"1125–Surnud","1105–Male":"1105–Surnud","1108–Male":"1108–Surnud","1125–Male":"1125–Surnud","1182–Male":"1182–Surnud","1091–Male":"1091–Surnud","1091":"1091","1105":"1105","1125":"1125","1182":"1182","1108":"1108"},"fi":{"1125–":"1125–Kuollut","1105–Male":"1105–Kuollut","1108–Male":"1108–Kuollut","1125–Male":"1125–Kuollut","1182–Male":"1182–Kuollut","1091–Male":"1091–Kuollut","1091":"1091","1105":"1105","1125":"1125","1182":"1182","1108":"1108"},"fr":{"1125–":"1125–Décédé","1105–Male":"1105–Décédé","1108–Male":"1108–Décédé","1125–Male":"1125–Décédé","1182–Male":"1182–Décédé","1091–Male":"1091–Décédé","1091":"1091","1105":"1105","1125":"1125","1182":"1182","1108":"1108","lifeSummary":"Gilbert de Ursewyke est né en 1125, fils de Bernulph de Ursewyke. Il a eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"1125–":"1125–Verstorben","1105–Male":"1105–Verstorben","1108–Male":"1108–Verstorben","1125–Male":"1125–Verstorben","1182–Male":"1182–Verstorben","1091–Male":"1091–Verstorben","1091":"1091","1105":"1105","1125":"1125","1182":"1182","1108":"1108","lifeSummary":"Gilbert de Ursewyke wurde 1125, als Sohn von Bernulph de Ursewyke geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"1125–":"1125–Desede","1105–Male":"1105–Desede","1108–Male":"1108–Desede","1125–Male":"1125–Desede","1